  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26605835_8_1590-1629",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1590-1629",
      "markText": "财富并不是一个确定不变的概念，事物的价值取决于某个特定时间点上他人的支付意愿。",
      "totalCount": 663,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26605835&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1590&rangeEnd=1629",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d14328d07195f90bd148088?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1590&rangeEnd=1629"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26605835_23_24995-25026",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "24995-25026",
      "markText": "我们已经找到了长久以来探寻的答案：财富是知识，它的起源是进化。",
      "totalCount": 368,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26605835&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=24995&rangeEnd=25026",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d14328d07195f90bd148088?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=24995&rangeEnd=25026"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26605835_6_3534-3582",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3534-3582",
      "markText": "我希望这本书是一本“周日上午指南”——其目标不在于告诉你具体应该怎么做，而在于改变你的思考方式。",
      "totalCount": 323,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26605835&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3534&rangeEnd=3582",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d14328d07195f90bd148088?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3534&rangeEnd=3582"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26605835_8_2108-2143",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2108-2143",
      "markText": "财富或许买不来幸福，但贫困却可以“买”到世界上数以百万计的民众的痛苦。",
      "totalCount": 280,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26605835&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2108&rangeEnd=2143",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d14328d07195f90bd148088?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2108&rangeEnd=2143"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26605835_8_8567-8649",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "8567-8649",
      "markText": "纽约人和亚诺玛米族人之间的显著差距，不是用美元衡量的“财富”上的400倍差距，而是纽约人经济与亚诺玛米族人经济的复杂性与多样性之间数百万倍，或者说8个数量级的差距。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26605835&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8567&rangeEnd=8649",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d14328d07195f90bd148088?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8567&rangeEnd=8649"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26605835_3_1144-1236",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1144-1236",
      "markText": "在得知拜因霍克家里一头牛都没有时，马赛族人显露出了遗憾的神情，同时还有一丝疑惑，他搞不明白这样穷困潦倒、家里一头牛都没有的人怎么有钱跑到村子里探访，还拥有相机这种看上去非常昂贵的东西。",
      "totalCount": 256,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26605835&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1144&rangeEnd=1236",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/d14328d07195f90bd148088?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1144&rangeEnd=1236"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26605835_3_2100-2180",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2100-2180",
      "markText": "经济本身是一个开放的、动态的非线性系统，并不会实现均衡状态，而经济人本身也是不完全理性的，经济本身是由众多个体组成的互动网络，是一种涌现现象，也是一个进化系统。",
      "totalCount": 234,
